Package: Friedman
Title: Simple Visualization Wrappers for Exploratory Data Analysis
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Animesh", "Singh", email = "animesh664@gmail.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A small set of wrapper functions built on ggplot2 for quickly
    making common exploratory plots like histograms, scatter plots, box plots,
    correlation heatmaps, and density comparisons with a single function
    call. Includes the ai_job_impact dataset and an S3 class for plot
    outputs.
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
Imports: ggplot2, rlang, stats
License: CC0
LazyData: true
Encoding: UTF-8
URL: https://github.com/Meshqc/Friedman
BugReports: https://github.com/Meshqc/Friedman/issues
Suggests: testthat (>= 3.0.0), knitr, rmarkdown
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
